To get the Google Maps URL for a specific location selected by the user on the map, you can listen for the map click event and generate the URL when the user clicks on a location.

Follow these steps to implement this feature in the "Views/Appointments/Create.cshtml" Razor view.

1. Add a new `<input>` element within the `<form>` to store the generated map URL:

```html
